data.description:
Welcome to this home in the quiet Southside neighborhood. This charming residence boasts a fully tiled interior, for easy maintenance. As you step into the living room, a cozy fireplace sets the tone for relaxation and warm gatherings.
The kitchen features a convenient breakfast bar, perfect for quick meals or casual dining. With a thoughtfully designed split floor plan, privacy is a priority, highlighted by the generously sized master bedroom. Enjoy the flexibility of an Arizona room, offering endless possibilities for a home office, exercise space, or a sun-soaked retreat
Step outside to discover a front courtyard, a delightful space for morning coffee or evening relaxation. Unwind in the hot tub, adding a touch of indulgence to your daily routine. The property also features side parking, providing ample space for a boat or RV enthusiasts. Experience the tranquility of a quiet neighborhood, coupled with the convenience of well-designed living spaces. Don't miss the opportunity to make this Southside gem your own. Schedule a showing today and envision the possibilities
that await you in this delightful abode.
